1
00:00:11,960 --> 00:00:15,410
♪The glass slipper's tale fades at midnight♪

2
00:00:15,930 --> 00:00:19,360
♪The prince with champagne is hunting his prey♪

3
00:00:19,760 --> 00:00:23,530
♪It's you, it's you, and it's you again♪

4
00:00:23,730 --> 00:00:25,220
♪Let's sing and dance♪

5
00:00:25,220 --> 00:00:26,760
♪Let's go happy♪

6
00:00:26,760 --> 00:00:30,110
♪Love is a crazy game♪

7
00:00:30,180 --> 00:00:34,050
♪Truth or lies, lost in desire♪

8
00:00:34,510 --> 00:00:37,880
♪No way out, sinking deeper♪

9
00:00:37,910 --> 00:00:40,860
♪Who surrenders, and still craves more?♪

10
00:00:41,180 --> 00:00:43,980
[Game of True Love]

11
00:00:44,100 --> 00:00:46,940
[Episode 36]

12
00:00:50,800 --> 00:00:52,050
Nuo, have you lost your mind?

13
00:00:53,110 --> 00:00:54,580
Don't you want to get back at me?

14
00:00:55,240 --> 00:00:56,290
Then do it.

15
00:00:56,960 --> 00:00:57,970
If mental torment

16
00:00:58,070 --> 00:00:59,500
isn't enough,

17
00:01:00,990 --> 00:01:01,900
tell me

18
00:01:02,160 --> 00:01:04,500
what will satisfy you!

19
00:01:04,600 --> 00:01:05,500
Let go!

20
00:01:45,080 --> 00:01:45,890
Don't worry.

21
00:01:48,670 --> 00:01:49,730
Once

22
00:01:51,720 --> 00:01:52,730
I've taken care of everything

23
00:01:52,750 --> 00:01:53,620
I need to,

24
00:01:55,390 --> 00:01:56,420
I'll let you go.

25
00:01:59,470 --> 00:02:00,420
What exactly are you planning?

26
00:02:02,960 --> 00:02:03,730
You don't need to know.

27
00:02:09,110 --> 00:02:10,370
Shen Jiahe,

28
00:02:12,480 --> 00:02:15,090
my mom is still in the hospital.

29
00:02:21,430 --> 00:02:22,460
I'll let you know

30
00:02:23,110 --> 00:02:24,300
the moment Aunt Rong wakes up.

31
00:03:00,110 --> 00:03:00,570
Hello?

32
00:03:01,200 --> 00:03:01,850
Hello, Mr. Shen.

33
00:03:02,590 --> 00:03:03,620
The driver's woken up.

34
00:03:03,960 --> 00:03:04,940
He insisted it was an accident.

35
00:03:06,200 --> 00:03:07,410
He was fired from Yuanfei

36
00:03:07,520 --> 00:03:08,500
for financial crimes.

37
00:03:09,200 --> 00:03:10,530
And now he just happens to hit Xu Mingli?

38
00:03:11,760 --> 00:03:12,770
That's a little too convenient.

39
00:03:15,480 --> 00:03:16,530
You think

40
00:03:17,110 --> 00:03:18,020
it was revenge?

41
00:03:19,960 --> 00:03:21,020
Someone must be behind this.

42
00:03:21,710 --> 00:03:22,180
Increase

43
00:03:22,240 --> 00:03:23,130
security

44
00:03:23,150 --> 00:03:23,810
around the hospital.

45
00:03:24,360 --> 00:03:25,180
Keep an eye on the house

46
00:03:25,200 --> 00:03:26,410
and watch out for suspicious people.

47
00:03:26,990 --> 00:03:28,500
Above all, make sure Nuo is safe.

48
00:03:29,150 --> 00:03:29,570
Okay.

49
00:03:29,920 --> 00:03:30,690
Understood, Mr. Shen.

50
00:03:45,960 --> 00:03:47,780
Shen Jiahe is definitely hiding something.

51
00:03:49,040 --> 00:03:50,650
I have to find a way to get out.

52
00:03:54,870 --> 00:03:55,690
If I eat all of this,

53
00:03:56,240 --> 00:03:57,500
my stomach issues will flare up for sure.

54
00:04:42,640 --> 00:04:43,450
It's nothing serious.

55
00:04:43,680 --> 00:04:44,690
Just take some fever-reducing medicine.

56
00:04:45,200 --> 00:04:46,700
If the fever persists,

57
00:04:46,830 --> 00:04:47,770
go to the hospital for an IV.

58
00:04:48,960 --> 00:04:50,250
The fever was triggered by gastroenteritis.

59
00:04:50,520 --> 00:04:50,980
Doctor...

60
00:04:51,000 --> 00:04:51,770
Avoid cold foods.

61
00:05:02,350 --> 00:05:02,860
How is she?

62
00:05:03,230 --> 00:05:04,180
No major issues, Mr. Shen.

63
00:05:04,440 --> 00:05:05,420
I'll be heading out now.

64
00:05:06,120 --> 00:05:06,660
Wait.

65
00:05:10,320 --> 00:05:11,300
Yes, Mr. Shen?

66
00:05:14,710 --> 00:05:15,940
Her stomach's been acting up lately.

67
00:05:16,320 --> 00:05:17,060
Prescribe her

68
00:05:17,120 --> 00:05:17,890
something mild to help

69
00:05:17,960 --> 00:05:18,570
with digestion.

70
00:05:20,390 --> 00:05:20,940
Of course.

71
00:05:22,710 --> 00:05:23,250
Thank you.

72
00:05:39,350 --> 00:05:40,860
Jiahe is keeping me trapped in the house.

73
00:05:41,200 --> 00:05:41,740
Help me.

74
00:05:42,470 --> 00:05:43,660
No. 1, Huaihai Road.

75
00:05:52,320 --> 00:05:53,010
Chi Ye,

76
00:05:53,910 --> 00:05:54,770
Nuo's doctor

77
00:05:54,830 --> 00:05:56,010
gave me a note.

78
00:05:56,440 --> 00:05:57,370
She says Shen Jiahe

79
00:05:57,470 --> 00:05:58,540
has her locked up at the house.

80
00:05:58,560 --> 00:05:59,540
She's asking for help.

81
00:06:00,270 --> 00:06:01,100
What should we do?

82
00:06:01,880 --> 00:06:02,860
Should we call the police?

83
00:06:03,350 --> 00:06:04,180
Calm down.

84
00:06:04,390 --> 00:06:05,100
I'll figure something out.

85
00:06:30,230 --> 00:06:31,180
Why aren't you eating?

86
00:06:32,960 --> 00:06:33,740
I'm not hungry.

87
00:06:34,760 --> 00:06:35,980
Even if you don't care about yourself,

88
00:06:36,320 --> 00:06:37,500
think about Aunt Rong.

89
00:06:42,710 --> 00:06:43,810
I want Aunt Pei to cook for me.

90
00:06:45,120 --> 00:06:46,100
She went back to her hometown.

91
00:06:46,230 --> 00:06:47,210
She won't be back for six months.

92
00:06:50,200 --> 00:06:51,420
Then give me my phone.

93
00:06:52,080 --> 00:06:52,810
I'll order something.

94
00:06:55,560 --> 00:06:56,500
You're still sick.

95
00:06:56,590 --> 00:06:57,370
No takeout.

96
00:07:04,000 --> 00:07:04,570
The new housekeeper

97
00:07:04,590 --> 00:07:05,540
will be here this afternoon.

98
00:07:06,880 --> 00:07:07,740
For now, just make do.

99
00:07:39,710 --> 00:07:40,370
Madam,

100
00:07:41,560 --> 00:07:42,100
do you know

101
00:07:42,120 --> 00:07:43,330
the house's door code?

102
00:07:48,120 --> 00:07:48,620
Madam?

103
00:07:49,390 --> 00:07:49,980
Madam?

104
00:08:02,350 --> 00:08:03,420
Why is Shen Jiahe

105
00:08:03,520 --> 00:08:04,940
keeping me locked up?

106
00:08:06,150 --> 00:08:07,570
What is he trying to do?

107
00:08:22,470 --> 00:08:23,940
Why won't you eat what Aunt Cui made?

108
00:08:24,710 --> 00:08:25,620
I told you,

109
00:08:26,270 --> 00:08:27,420
I want Sichuan food.

110
00:08:27,760 --> 00:08:28,570
You're still sick.

111
00:08:28,680 --> 00:08:29,540
You can't have spicy food.

112
00:08:29,560 --> 00:08:30,500
I don't care.

113
00:08:38,320 --> 00:08:39,420
Either that, or I go on a hunger strike.

114
00:08:56,200 --> 00:08:56,660
I'll find you

115
00:08:56,680 --> 00:08:57,660
another housekeeper.

116
00:09:10,080 --> 00:09:10,850
Here, Miss Xu.

117
00:09:15,630 --> 00:09:16,330
Miss Xu,

118
00:09:16,710 --> 00:09:17,970
Mr. Chi Ye sent me.

119
00:09:18,200 --> 00:09:18,900
I've already sent him

120
00:09:18,920 --> 00:09:19,780
the door code.

121
00:09:21,440 --> 00:09:22,140
That's great.

122
00:09:29,960 --> 00:09:31,970
Why are you drinking so fast?

123
00:09:46,440 --> 00:09:48,180
Is he onto something?

124
00:09:51,280 --> 00:09:52,730
Aren't you going to work today?

125
00:09:53,750 --> 00:09:55,940
I'll be working from home from now on.

126
00:10:16,040 --> 00:10:17,780
Chi Ye is waiting outside tonight.

127
00:10:18,400 --> 00:10:19,780
This is my one chance.

128
00:10:35,080 --> 00:10:35,660
Nuo!

129
00:10:36,440 --> 00:10:37,900
Be careful. Watch out for the glass.

130
00:10:40,320 --> 00:10:41,330
Why did you drink so much?

131
00:10:43,960 --> 00:10:45,380
I miss my mom.

132
00:10:48,870 --> 00:10:49,570
I don't even know

133
00:10:49,630 --> 00:10:51,020
how she's doing.

134
00:10:53,630 --> 00:10:54,940
I want to see her.

135
00:10:57,160 --> 00:10:57,730
Nuo,

136
00:11:00,350 --> 00:11:01,140
don't worry.

137
00:11:01,440 --> 00:11:02,690
Aunt Rong's condition is stable.

138
00:11:03,560 --> 00:11:04,450
Starting tomorrow,

139
00:11:05,040 --> 00:11:05,940
I'll have someone

140
00:11:06,040 --> 00:11:07,570
send you video updates every day.

141
00:11:21,630 --> 00:11:23,180
Stop drinking. You just got better.

142
00:11:26,080 --> 00:11:26,970
I want to drink.

143
00:11:29,440 --> 00:11:30,940
And you're drinking with me.

144
00:12:01,350 --> 00:12:02,420
Shen Jiahe,

145
00:12:05,630 --> 00:12:06,780
to be honest,

146
00:12:08,400 --> 00:12:09,850
I wish I could kill you.

147
00:12:13,630 --> 00:12:14,730
Do you know

148
00:12:15,870 --> 00:12:17,060
why I'm even sitting here

149
00:12:17,110 --> 00:12:18,540
drinking with you?

150
00:12:19,680 --> 00:12:20,420
Why?

151
00:12:21,560 --> 00:12:23,060
Because I plan to get you drunk

152
00:12:24,870 --> 00:12:25,940
so I can escape.

153
00:12:27,560 --> 00:12:28,180
Alright.

154
00:12:29,230 --> 00:12:30,420
Go ahead. Get me drunk.

155
00:12:52,230 --> 00:12:53,210
Do I have to feed you?

156
00:13:03,400 --> 00:13:04,380
You think you can get me drunk?

157
00:13:05,110 --> 00:13:06,060
You don't have what it takes.

158
00:13:10,560 --> 00:13:11,260
That's true.

159
00:13:13,750 --> 00:13:15,730
Compared to you,

160
00:13:16,870 --> 00:13:18,260
I have no patience for long games.

161
00:13:23,590 --> 00:13:24,730
I was so stupid.

162
00:13:26,440 --> 00:13:27,690
I gave you my heart

163
00:13:27,710 --> 00:13:28,570
so easily.

164
00:13:40,960 --> 00:13:41,940
Enough. Stop drinking.

165
00:13:42,440 --> 00:13:43,570
Can't I just numb myself

166
00:13:43,680 --> 00:13:44,490
for a bit?

167
00:13:56,350 --> 00:13:57,810
I've been doing a lot of thinking.

168
00:13:59,320 --> 00:14:01,020
But no matter how hard I try, I don't understand.

169
00:14:01,750 --> 00:14:02,850
Why is it my mom

170
00:14:02,870 --> 00:14:04,060
who's in a coma,

171
00:14:04,470 --> 00:14:05,780
not Xu Mingli?

172
00:14:16,470 --> 00:14:17,300
Shen Jiahe,

173
00:14:20,560 --> 00:14:21,450
I hate you.

174
00:14:23,830 --> 00:14:25,140
I hate Xu Mingli too.

175
00:14:28,080 --> 00:14:29,610
The two of you have brought me

176
00:14:30,920 --> 00:14:32,020
nothing but pain.

177
00:14:58,710 --> 00:15:00,900
You're right.

178
00:15:22,510 --> 00:15:23,420
Nuo...

179
00:15:51,960 --> 00:15:53,140
Shen Jiahe,

180
00:15:56,560 --> 00:15:57,660
maybe we were just

181
00:15:57,710 --> 00:15:58,780
never meant to be.

182
00:16:04,630 --> 00:16:06,380
I hope you can let go of your hatred

183
00:16:08,110 --> 00:16:09,380
and live a good life.

184
00:17:00,920 --> 00:17:01,490
Nuo!

185
00:17:01,680 --> 00:17:02,330
Chi Ye!

186
00:17:27,750 --> 00:17:28,620
Mr. Shen, you're awake.

187
00:17:28,960 --> 00:17:29,450
I'm sorry.

188
00:17:29,840 --> 00:17:31,050
Last night, Miss Xu...

189
00:17:31,200 --> 00:17:31,730
I know.

190
00:17:33,510 --> 00:17:34,940
She had someone send this over.

191
00:17:43,380 --> 00:17:53,500
[Breakup gift]

192
00:18:30,020 --> 00:18:35,520
♪I love you, love you, love you♪

193
00:18:35,520 --> 00:18:44,390
♪So deep that I forget who I am♪

194
00:18:44,560 --> 00:18:50,260
♪I miss you, miss you, miss you♪
